<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{#if approved}}‚úÖ Webhook Approved{{else}}‚ùå Webhook Rejected{{/if}} - {{webhookName}}</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{#if approved}}#10B981 0%, #059669 100%{{else}}#EF4444 0%, #DC2626 100%{{/if}});
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{#if approved}}#10B981 0%, #059669 50%, #047857 100%{{else}}#EF4444 0%, #DC2626 50%, #B91C1C 100%{{/if}});
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.7; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(180deg); opacity: 1; }
    }
    .status-icon {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .header-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .header-subtitle {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      font-size: 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      background: white;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .intro-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .webhook-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{#if approved}}#f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%{{else}}#fef2f2 0%, #fecaca 100%{{/if}});
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-left: 5px solid {{#if approved}}#10B981{{else}}#EF4444{{/if}};
    }
    .webhook-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .webhook-icon-small {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{#if approved}}#10B981 0%, #059669 100%{{else}}#EF4444 0%, #DC2626 100%{{/if}});
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }
    .webhook-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: {{#if approved}}#065f46{{else}}#991b1b{{/if}};
    }
    .webhook-details {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
    }
    .detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .detail-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 14px;
      min-width: 120px;
    }
    .detail-value {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: right;
      word-break: break-all;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .status-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{#if approved}}#d1fae5 0%, #a7f3d0 100%{{else}}#fee2e2 0%, #fecaca 100%{{/if}});
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-left: 5px solid {{#if approved}}#10B981{{else}}#EF4444{{/if}};
    }
    .status-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: {{#if approved}}#065f46{{else}}#991b1b{{/if}};
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .status-icon-small {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    .status-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: {{#if approved}}#047857{{else}}#b91c1c{{/if}};
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .admin-notes {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #6b7280;
    }
    .admin-notes-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .admin-notes-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .quick-actions {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: {{#if approved}}1fr 1fr{{else}}1fr{{/if}};
      gap: 15px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .action-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .primary-action {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{#if approved}}#10B981 0%, #059669 100%{{else}}#6b7280 0%, #4b5563 100%{{/if}});
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba({{#if approved}}16, 185, 129{{else}}107, 114, 128{{/if}}, 0.3);
    }
    .secondary-action {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
      color: #374151;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    }
    .next-steps {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2937 0%, #111827 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .next-steps-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: {{#if approved}}#d1fae5{{else}}#fecaca{{/if}};
    }
    .next-steps-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .next-steps-list li {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .next-steps-list li::before {
      content: '{{#if approved}}‚úì{{else}}!{{/if}}';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: {{#if approved}}#60a5fa{{else}}#f87171{{/if}};
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f7fafc;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #718096;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .footer-links {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer-link {
      color: {{#if approved}}#10B981{{else}}#6b7280{{/if}};
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0 15px;
    }
    .footer-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-container { margin: 10px; border-radius: 15px; }
      .header { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .quick-actions { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .detail-row { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
      .detail-value { text-align: left; margin-top: 5px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="status-icon">
        {{#if approved}}
        <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
          <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/>
        </svg>
        {{else}}
        <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
          <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"/>
        </svg>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
      <h1 class="header-title">{{#if approved}}Webhook Approved!{{else}}Webhook Rejected{{/if}}</h1>
      <p class="header-subtitle">{{#if approved}}Your webhook is now active and ready{{else}}Your webhook request has been declined{{/if}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="greeting">Hi {{userName}}! üëã</h2>
      
      <p class="intro-text">
        {{#if approved}}
        Great news! Your webhook "<strong>{{webhookName}}</strong>" has been approved by administrator <strong>{{adminName}}</strong> and is now active. 
        It will start receiving data from form submissions immediately.
        {{else}}
        We regret to inform you that your webhook "<strong>{{webhookName}}</strong>" has been rejected by administrator <strong>{{adminName}}</strong>. 
        Please review the feedback below and consider creating a new webhook with the necessary adjustments.
        {{/if}}
      </p>

      <div class="webhook-card">
        <div class="webhook-header">
          <div class="webhook-icon-small">
            {{#if approved}}
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
              <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/>
            </svg>
            {{else}}
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
              <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"/>
            </svg>
            {{/if}}
          </div>
          <h3 class="webhook-title">{{webhookName}}</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="webhook-details">
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Endpoint URL:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{webhookUrl}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Form:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{formTitle}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Status:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{#if approved}}‚úÖ Approved & Active{{else}}‚ùå Rejected{{/if}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Reviewed by:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{adminName}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{#if adminNotes}}
      <div class="admin-notes">
        <div class="admin-notes-title">Administrator Notes:</div>
        <div class="admin-notes-text">"{{adminNotes}}"</div>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <div class="status-section">
        <h3 class="status-title">
          {{#if approved}}
          <svg class="status-icon-small" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#10B981">
            <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/>
          </svg>
          Webhook is Now Active
          {{else}}
          <svg class="status-icon-small" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#EF4444">
            <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"/>
          </svg>
          Webhook Request Declined
          {{/if}}
        </h3>
        <p class="status-text">
          {{#if approved}}
          Your webhook is now live and will receive data from form submissions. You can test it, monitor delivery logs, 
          and manage settings through your dashboard.
          {{else}}
          Your webhook will not receive any data. If you believe this was an error or would like to address the concerns, 
          please contact your administrator or create a new webhook with the necessary modifications.
          {{/if}}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="quick-actions">
        {{#if approved}}
        <a href="{{webhookUrl_manage}}" class="action-button primary-action">
          Manage Webhook
        </a>
        <a href="{{webhookUrl_logs}}" class="action-button secondary-action">
          View Logs
        </a>
        {{else}}
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="action-button primary-action">
          Go to Dashboard
        </a>
        {{/if}}
      </div>

      <div class="next-steps">
        <h3 class="next-steps-title">{{#if approved}}What you can do now:{{else}}Next steps:{{/if}}</h3>
        <ul class="next-steps-list">
          {{#if approved}}
          <li>Test your webhook to ensure it's working correctly</li>
          <li>Monitor delivery logs for any issues</li>
          <li>Submit test forms to see webhook data in action</li>
          <li>Configure additional settings if needed</li>
          {{else}}
          <li>Review the administrator's feedback above</li>
          <li>Contact your administrator for clarification if needed</li>
          <li>Create a new webhook addressing the concerns</li>
          <li>Ensure your endpoint meets security requirements</li>
          {{/if}}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p class="footer-text">
        This email was sent from {{appName}}. {{#if approved}}Your webhook is now ready to receive data!{{else}}If you have questions about this decision, please contact your administrator.{{/if}}
      </p>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="footer-link">Dashboard</a>
        <a href="{{webhookUrl_manage}}" class="footer-link">Webhook Settings</a>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-text" style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0;">
        ¬© 2025 {{appName}}. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 